Manga
A manga adaptation illustrated by Kamito began serialization on the Manga Doa'' app on April 23, 2021. The manga's chapters have been collected by Mag Garden into five  volumes as of November 2025.
In March 2025, Seven Seas Entertainment announced that they had licensed the manga for English publication, with the first volume set to release in January 2026.
